    rdfs:label "Chandrashekar Ramanathan" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:research "Education :Ph.D. (Mississippi State University) Professor Chandrashekar Ramanathan is a faculty member at IIIT-B (International Institute of Information Technology Bangalore) since 2007 serving as professor, researcher and administrator. He has been working in the field of Computing for over 25 years in various capacities across industry and academia. He has been associated with IIITB for over 15 years where he has been teaching and carrying out research in diverse areas. His expertise lies in t" ;
