    rdfs:label "Dinesh Babu Jayagopi" ;
    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:research "Education :Ph.D. (École Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne) Prof. Dinesh Babu Jayagopi is currently the Head of Data Science and AI (DSAI) department at IIIT Bangalore, where he heads the Multimodal Perception Lab.  His research interests are in Audio-Visual Signal Processing, Machine Learning, and Social Computing. He obtained his doctorate from Ecole Polytechnic Federale Lausanne (EPFL), Switzerland, beginning of 2011. He received the National Teachers Award from the President of India in the " ;
    edu:source "https://www.iiitb.ac.in/faculty/dinesh-babu-jayagopi" .

