    edu:belongsTo iiitb:iiitb ;
    edu:description "Applications for the Academic Year 2026–27 are now open. [March 19, 2026]: Applications for the Academic Year 2026–27 are open.Candidates can apply via the linkhttps://admissions.iiitb.net/ You can download a FREEIIIT-B admission brochure. The minimum qualification for admission to the M.Tech (CSE) programme is 65% in four-year bachelor's degree in engineering (i.e. B.E., B.Tech., or equivalent) in any one of the following (or equivalent) branches. Final-year students expecting to graduate byJuly 2026may also apply. Admissions to the M.Tech (CSE) programme is on the basis of performance in the GATE examination. GATE scores (valid as of June 1, 2026) in CS - Computer Science and Information Technology will be considered for admission to the M.Tech. (CSE) programme. There is no fixed cut-off" ;
