      Learning Theory,Computational Complexity. Mahima is a research scholar at IIIT Bangalore, specializing in software
      sustainability. Her current research focuses on developing metrics to
      assess """,
        """Sujit's interest broadly lie in the formal aspects of software engineering. He is particularly interested in applying formal 
			techniques to improve the productivity of software engineers in various engineering domains. The domains he has worked in are: Sujit's current research efforts are in the development of advanced techniques of testing embedded software systems, formal specification of web-applications, and specification based testing of web-applications. First of all, let me thank the s""" ;
